_:cb1e5b19abc5df7cf6ac7bf001761f093d436640701a7021115b541f0927b800469 <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> "Risk assessment must reference the critical-to-quality factor it assesses." .
_:cb1e5b19abc5df7cf6ac7bf001761f093d436640701a7021115b541f0927b800469 <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#minCount> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> .
